<h1>How to play</h1>

<p>You’ll use this device to play!</p>

<ul>
  <li>We’ll ask you a question!</li>
  <li>You’ll type your answer. Try to sound correct!</li>
  <li>You’ll try to pick the right answer among those your friends answered.</li>
  <li>You get a point for answering correctly.</li>
  <li>You get a point for each time your answer is chosen!</li>
